@node "Document_6" "The history"
@{b}@{u}The history of Index2Guide@{ub}@{uu}

@{b}1.3@{ub} A lot of things were done:
    *Bugs were fixed
    *Now allocates memory instead of opening files in RAM
    *Faster (than it would have been if files were opened in RAM)
    *Now converts Recent-files as well as Index-files
    *Nice GUI was added
    *Writes descriptions of drawers if the TREE-files is present
    *Program checks if the file actually is an AmiNet-file or not

@{b}1.0@{ub} First public release
@endnode

